---
title: Korean Style BBQ Pork Noodles with Pepper, Lime and Peanuts
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Korean Style BBQ Pork Noodles in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R13_W22_UK_R17179-3_Main_low-36ddbea8.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/6602e2ef8928bc357c2d2ef4.pdf
author: Lily Stevens
servings: 2
time required: 20m
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/korean-style-bbq-pork-noodles-6602e2ef8928bc357c2d2ef4
